title: Hot Dog Caper Serves Up Food and Fun (California State Polytechnic University, Pomona)
text: ( Source : California State Polytechnic University, Pomona ) Grooving to 1960s tunes by the band Aquarius , Cal Poly Pomona students, staff and faculty celebrated the start of the new school year at the 32nd annual Hot Dog Caper. Participants
